findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract has various owner privileges that can be exploited if the owner is not renounced, including rebasing, changing sellMultiplier, trading and launch status, blacklist mode, maxRoomRent value, cooldown settings, pair address, master address, withdrawing BEP20 tokens, and more.

findings.title: DoS with block gas limit
findings.description: The contract is vulnerable to Denial of Service (DoS) attacks due to block gas limit.
